{"data":[{"date":"23:36 10/08","title":"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd \u2018Messi m\u1edbi\u2019, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/phot-lo-messi-moi-olympic-indonesia-trieu-tap-sao-u40-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Olympic Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Messi m\u1edbi, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Messi m\u1edbi, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/XT5gRGy6Ah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Alberto Goncalves l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n\u00a0Olympic Indonesia t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 V\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alberto Goncalves, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 38 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alberto Goncalves l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u1ed1c Brazil. Anh \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Indonesia trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sriwijaya. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 6 l\u1ea7n 'khai h\u1ecfa'.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Alberto Goncalves \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Alberto Goncalves, m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u1ed1c H\u00e0 Lan, Stefano Lilipaly v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Andritany Ardiyasa. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a \"Messi m\u1edbi\" Egy Maulana Vikri.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, Indonesia n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i Palestine, Hong Kong (TQ), \u0110\u00e0i B\u1eafc Trung Hoa v\u00e0 L\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2221","checkdouble":"194209"},{"date":"23:55 10/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/truyen-thong-nhat-ban-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t t\u1eebng \u2018\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i, n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u01b0\u1edbc\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.</h2><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c v\u1eeba l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Asiad 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal, Olympic Pakistan. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc c\u0169ng xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Truyen-thong-Nhat-Ban-noi-gi-ve-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 t\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf trong th\u1eddi gian qua. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qoly c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd n\u00e0y m\u00f4 t\u1ea3: \"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n khi m\u00e0 trong tay HLV Hajime th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Olympic 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 v\u1ecb \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u0103m nay. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u1ecd\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Qoly vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 hai ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 sau: \u00a0\u201cTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf K-League. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i J-League 2 nh\u01b0ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18-168-194207.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/10/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18-168-194207.html\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194206.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194206.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2220","checkdouble":"194210"},{"date":"23:56 10/08","title":"Alexis Sanchez tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 n\u1eeda n\u0103m kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 \u1edf Old Trafford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/alexis-sanchez-trai-long-ve-nua-nam-khon-kho-o-old-trafford.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd do m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pogba trong ng\u00e0y \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd do m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pogba trong ng\u00e0y \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n:<br>\r\n- MU: Pogba 3' (pen), Shaw 83'<br>\r\n- Leicester City: Vardy 90'+2<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nMan Utd: </strong>De Gea; Darmian, Bailly,  Lindelof, Shaw; Pogba (Fellaini 84'), A Pereira, Fred (McTominay 76');  Mata,  Rashford (Lukaku 67'), Sanchez.<br>\r\n<strong>Leicester:</strong> Schmeichel; Ricardo, Morgan, Maguire, Chilwell. Amartey (Ghezzal 63'), Silva,  Ndidi, Maddison (Vardy 63'), Gray, Iheanacho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2219","checkdouble":"194211"},{"date":"00:26 11/08","title":"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/12/hlv-truong-clb-thai-son-nam-noi-gi-khi-vao-chung-ket-futsal-cac-clb-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, HLV Miguel Rodrigo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m 6-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Lebanon, Bank of Beirut.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/12/tan-hlv-miguel-rodrigo-futsal-viet-nam-van-thua-thai-lan.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Miguel Rodrigo t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn 3-1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam ch\u01a1i b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh v\u00e0 ghi li\u1ec1n 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Qu\u1ed1c H\u01b0ng (29') v\u00e0 c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Th\u00e0nh T\u00edn (32', 35' v\u00e0 36') gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 5-3. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 6-5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u1ede c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0 2017 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Miguel Rodrigo, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T futsal Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 cho hay: \"T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 3-1. S\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p CLB \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Iran, Mes Sungun Varzaghan. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CLB Nafit Al-wasat 3-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h ng\u00e0y 12/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight: Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam 6-5 Beirut<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/10/Thai-Son-Nam-FC-6-5-Bank-of-Beirut.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2218","checkdouble":"194214"},{"date":"06:46 11/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/21/Tien-dao-Michy-Batshuayi-Co-hoi-cuoi-cung-hinh-anh-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01a1i\u201d Michy Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d Valencia trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Antonio Conte tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Michy Batshuayi lang b\u1ea1t sang \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh thu\u00ea cho Borussia Dortmund v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 9 b\u00e0n/14 tr\u1eadn.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/21/Tien-dao-Michy-Batshuayi-Co-hoi-cuoi-cung-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi Chelsea hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ra h\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Olivier Giroud \u0111\u1ebfn Alvaro Morata. Kh\u00f4ng, s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Batshuayi r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c khi anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Chelsea l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Valencia theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb CLB th\u00e0nh London nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t video clip \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i n\u1ed9i dung v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e0n d\u01a1i. \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01a1i\u201d (Batman) l\u00e0 bi\u1ec7t danh c\u1ee7a Batshuayi, trong khi Valencia l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Batshuayi \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a t\u00e2n HLV Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho hai t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Tammy Abraham v\u00e0 Callum Hudson-Odoi, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng trung phong \u0111\u00e0n anh kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Giroud v\u00e0 Morata.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i nay, Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2217","checkdouble":"194218"},{"date":"04:14 11/08","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/video-tong-hop-mu-21-leicester-vong-1-premier-league-201819.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd do m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pogba trong ng\u00e0y \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd do m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pogba trong ng\u00e0y \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n:<br>\r\n- MU: Pogba 3' (pen), Shaw 83'<br>\r\n- Leicester City: Vardy 90'+2<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nMan Utd: </strong>De Gea; Darmian, Bailly,  Lindelof, Shaw; Pogba (Fellaini 84'), A Pereira, Fred (McTominay 76');  Mata,  Rashford (Lukaku 67'), Sanchez.<br>\r\n<strong>Leicester:</strong> Schmeichel; Ricardo, Morgan, Maguire, Chilwell. Amartey (Ghezzal 63'), Silva,  Ndidi, Maddison (Vardy 63'), Gray, Iheanacho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2216","checkdouble":"194219"},{"date":"04:32 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n di\u1ec5n ra trong \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Leicester \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 thua c\u1ea3 2 (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Ryan Babel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Pogba-thuc-hien-thanh-cong-penalty-cho-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Jose Mourinho b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 18 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV (th\u1eafng 11, h\u00f2a 7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ri\u00eang t\u1ea1i Premier League, Mourinho th\u1eafng 9 trong s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n (h\u00f2a 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Luke Shaw c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 67 cho h\u1ecd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- M.U c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 123 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Premier League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford khi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Trong c\u1ea3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Leicester \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- M.U b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester (th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 8 trong 9 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gh\u00e9 th\u0103m s\u00e2n Old Trafford (h\u00f2a 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Premier League, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t (18).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- M.U b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 10 sau 11 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 6 (th\u1eafng 7, h\u00f2a 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 21 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh khi ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 6 (th\u1eafng 15, h\u00f2a 6).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&amp;autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2215","checkdouble":"194220"},{"date":"05:38 11/08","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-21-cua-mu-truoc-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c Man United \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Leicester City v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. C\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin, trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, HLV Jose Mourinho l\u1eadp danh s\u00e1ch 5 trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 cho Manchester United. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, cho t\u1edbi khi chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c CLB Premier League \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. M.U c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho \u00f4ng tri\u1ec3n khai phong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eb7t, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/M.U-dan-truoc-Leicester-1-0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, M.U v\u1eabn h\u1edf ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David De Gea m\u1edbi c\u1ee9u h\u1ecd tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, trong th\u1ebf tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Maddison b\u00ean ph\u00eda Leicester. B\u1eb1ng ma thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean c\u00f9ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Song khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ngai v\u00e0ng Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, xem ra Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 27 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leicester v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean M.U, Jonny Evans \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Leicester h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Anh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong khi 2 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Filip Benkovic v\u00e0 Caglar Soyuncu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean ch\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n Leicester v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-2-1-cua-MU-truoc-Leicester-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Leicester khi\u1ebfn M.U kh\u00e1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 1, Leicester nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Cho t\u1edbi chung cu\u1ed9c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (53,8%). N\u1ebfu Maddison hay Iheanacho nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n h\u01a1n, B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Shaw ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau nh\u00f3m \u201cBig Six\u201d, Leicester c\u00f9ng Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19 c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2m l\u00fd B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng b\u00e0n. S\u1ef1 h\u1ee5t h\u1eabng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Trong kho\u1ea3ng 1 th\u00e1ng qua, HLV Mourinho li\u00ean t\u1ee5c k\u00eau than v\u00e0 khi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua s\u1eafm kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0o, n\u00f3 lan t\u1ecfa \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t tr\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111i c\u00e1i d\u1edbp m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Mourinho. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n. T\u00ednh c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mou l\u00e0m cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xung quanh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, M.U lu\u00f4n t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y mong manh. Cho t\u1edbi t\u1eadn gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu. Th\u1eadt may Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, song h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i hay kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng Sanchez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u201cC\u1eadu b\u00e9 k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u\u201d m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Sanchez l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez tran M.U vs Leicester\" title=\"Sanchez tran M.U vs Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Sanchez-tran-M.U-vs-Leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sanchez l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, m\u1ecdi pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sanchez \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf. Ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty cho M.U v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, anh c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam 4 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 cho Romelu Lukaku. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Sanchez l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Leicester khi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, M.U ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 68 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u00edt h\u01a1n 3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong t\u1ed1p 4 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Arsenal. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Sanchez, h\u1ecd \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Maddison g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, song James Maddison th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. M\u1edbi 21 tu\u1ed5i, ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn t\u1eeb m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 m\u00e0 Ryiad Mahrez \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i song anh tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maddison cua Leicester\" title=\"Maddison cua Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Maddison-cua-Leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Maddison c\u1ee7a Leicester t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Demarai Gray, Maddison l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Leicester tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Tr\u00f4ng c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Norwich nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u binh d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i \u201cth\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba\u201d Old Trafford c\u1ee7a M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu De Gea kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n, Maddison \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i CLB m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi 45 ph\u00fat. Duy tr\u00ec v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t huy phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 1996 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Leicester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Thong-tin-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2214","checkdouble":"194222"},{"date":"06:08 11/08","title":"\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester, Mourinho ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/danh-bai-leicester-mourinho-ca-ngoi-suc-manh-tap-the-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat Leicester</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City \u1edf tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 2018/19. Sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp ng\u01b0\u1eddi Wes Morgan tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i tr\u00fang tay m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 Daniel Amartey trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 Paul Pogba kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Leicester v\u00f9ng l\u00ean d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch d\u1ed3n M.U v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-sau-tran-dau-MU-2-1-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i\u00a0Leicester 2-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Leicester t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu s\u1eafc b\u00e9n c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap M.U \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 83. Luke Shaw \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00fap h\u1ecd nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Jamie Vardy ph\u00fat 90+2 tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Chung cu\u1ed9c M.U \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ca ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" title=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Mourinho-tran-M.U-vs-Leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRichard Scudamore (Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Premier League) ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi 6 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i 3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng Anthony Martial, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. Paul Pogba kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i 90 ph\u00fat, Fred c\u0169ng v\u1eady. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01a1n. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec mong \u0111\u1ee3i. Leicester r\u1ea5t hay trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2213","checkdouble":"194223"},{"date":"06:37 11/08","title":"Luke Shaw n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-noi-gi-sau-khi-ghi-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a M.U v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u00e2ng l\u00e2ng sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Luke Shaw t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Antonio Valencia r\u1ed3i Marcos Rojo b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Ashley Young ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u1eadu World Cup 2018, c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Man United kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf khi HLV Jose Mourinho bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Luke Shaw cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00edch danh. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9, th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Luke-Shaw-ghi-ban-dau-tien-cho-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. C\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Southampton \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19. Anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho M.U v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 ph\u00fat 90+2 c\u1ee7a Jamie Vardy tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nH\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 67 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho M.U tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Southampton n\u0103m 2014, Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Juan Mata, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Leicester.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194220.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194220.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec quan tr\u1ecdng. Vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d, Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Sky Sports. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 xoay x\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 suy ng\u1eabm, l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Man United v\u1edbi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2212","checkdouble":"194224"},{"date":"15:38 10/08","title":"MU kh\u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9, Smalling v\u1eabn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/27/mu-khong-mua-sam-ram-ro-smalling-van-thach-thuc-nhung-doi-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bi-quan-ve-kha-nang-mua-them-nguoi-172-194120.html\" target=\"_blank\">BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</span>.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Chris-Smalling-phat-bieu-ve-MU-truoc-mua-giai-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fred v\u00e0 Dalot. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam duy nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld, Yerry Mina, Jerome Boateng, Harry Magui, Willian, Ivan Perisic, Sergej Milinkovic-Savic... l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf, nh\u01b0ng BL\u0110 M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, M.U m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chi ra kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" title=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-18,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling tin M.U v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn, song v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n M.U v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng M.U b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p do kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng theo t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p M.U, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2211","checkdouble":"194177"},{"date":"15:47 10/08","title":"Emery \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-phat-bieu-ve-muc-tieu-cua-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, nh\u01b0ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt phong c\u00e1ch.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i t\u1ed1p 4 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, HLV Arsenen Wenger tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal. M\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf ra v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh d\u00f9 nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-phat-bieu-ve-muc-tieu-cua-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a CLB l\u00e0 v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u01a1i v\u00ec c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u\u201d, Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00f9ng nhau c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i cho C\u0110V c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEmery \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal t\u1eeb Wenger. \u00d4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u201cPhong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed7i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3i lu\u00f4n d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n l\u00e0m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian, nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n hi\u1ec7n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dau-la-ban-hop-dong-xuat-sac-nhat-mua-he-2018-172-194147.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal-172-194121.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-buon-vui-lan-lon-vu-aaron-ramsey-172-194087.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea bu\u1ed3n vui l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n v\u1ee5 Aaron Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-giu-chan-ramsey-vi-chuyen-mon-va-mot-loi-khang-dinh-172-194026.html\">Arsenal gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Ramsey: V\u00ec chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2210","checkdouble":"194178"},{"date":"16:13 10/08","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-tre-khang-dinh-se-giup-do-tan-binh-fred-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eadn may \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi anh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Th\u00e0nh Chung g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u1ed7i h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 ngay trong s\u00e1ng nay, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/27/Sep-HAGL-noi-gi-khi-Minh-Vuong-nhan-\u2018ve-vot\u2019-cua-thay-Park-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u0103ng.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t: \u201cS\u00e1ng nay, anh L\u00ea Ho\u00e0i Anh \u2013 T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd VFF \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi CLB v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang-seo g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. Hi\u1ec7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh ra H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 bay \u0111i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngay trong chi\u1ec1u nay\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may c\u1eadu ta l\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u201d, v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t t\u1ed1t, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o, \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \"Open Sans\", sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2209","checkdouble":"194180"},{"date":"16:12 10/08","title":"Th\u00eam 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/12/them-1-cau-thu-hagl-duoc-bo-sung-len-tuyen-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park g\u1ecdi thay th\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/10/Minh-Vuong-duoc-goi-bo-sung-len-tuyen-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo\u00a0g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a,<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-co-them-ca-chan-thuong-truoc-khi-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194157.html\" target=\"_blank\"> h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u qua 9/8. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf, v\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a HAGL.</div>\r\n<p>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u00f4ng Park ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n, qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ed3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n Thanh v\u00e0 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, trong khi s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, h\u00f4m nay (10/8) U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11/8. Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 14, 16 v\u00e0 19/8.\u00a0V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, O. Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\">B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)\u00a0<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2208","checkdouble":"194181"},{"date":"16:23 10/08","title":"B\u1ecb nh\u0103m nhe c\u01b0\u1edbp Modric, Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n Inter","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/17/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric b\u1ecb Inter Milan ve v\u00e3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 \u0110T Croatia, Inter Milan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean. H\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Inter s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho Modric m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro, g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111ang l\u0129nh t\u1ea1i Real (6,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro) trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Nerazzurri c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Trung Qu\u1ed1c khi mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Real-Madrid-dam-phan-mua-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Inter mu\u1ed1n Modric c\u1ee7a Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Real t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a Inter Milan. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Los Blancos \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Karim Benzema ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t k\u00e9m duy\u00ean. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Icardi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi t\u1edbi 100 b\u00e0n sau 159 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Inter k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Icardi\" title=\"tien dao Icardi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/17/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2017/18, Icardi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh ghi t\u1edbi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Inter ch\u1ec9 sau 34 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie A, \u0111\u1ed3ng Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng Ciro Immobile. \u0110i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Inter l\u00e0 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Icardi trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\">Thibaut Courtois CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-chelsea-muon-duoc-kovacic-tu-real-172-194124.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-courtois-toi-real-madrid-172-194113.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-muon-giu-chan-luka-modric-180-194111.html\">Real n\u00edu k\u00e9o Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-0908-180-194097.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 09/08</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2207","checkdouble":"194183"}]}